//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自从出现在 Emerald Fennell 的新电影中后，这部 2001 年的流行歌曲在 TikTok 上疯传，并吸引了大批 Z 世代新粉丝</p><p>Sophie Ellis-Bextor 的《Murder On The Dancefloor》继《Saltburn》场景首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-ellis-bextors-murder-on-the-dancefloor-to-return-to-top-40-chart-after-saltburn-scene-3565573">后重返排行榜前 40 名</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="索菲·埃利斯-贝斯特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-at-the-premiere-of-22Saltburn22-held-at-The-Theatre-at-Ace-Hotel-on-November-14-2023-in-Los-Angeles-California.-Photo-by-Alberto-RodriguezVariety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sophie-ellis-bextor">索菲·埃利斯-贝斯特 (Sophie Ellis-Bextor)</a>的流行经典歌曲《舞池谋杀案》(Murder On The Dancefloor) 本周将重新进入英国单曲排行榜前 40 名，其索尔特本 ( <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/saltburn">Saltburn</a></em> ) 风格的复兴仍在继续。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/saltburn-music-indie-pop-noughties-mgmt-bloc-party-3537593">“Saltburn”的声音：电影中五首完美的二十世纪九十年代独立摇滚歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>在埃默拉尔德·芬内尔 (Emerald Fennell) 的新片中，巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 饰演的奥利弗·奎克 (Oliver Quick) 伴随着 2001 年热门流行音乐的配乐在一座乡村宅邸中裸体跳舞，为这部新片画上句号。</p><p>从那时起，它在 TikTok 上赢得了大批新的 Z 世代粉丝，其主题标签的观看次数超过 3850 万次，这首歌被包含在 25 万个视频中。埃利斯-贝斯特本人也加入了这一潮流，在 TikTok 视频中重现了基奥根的舞蹈，您可以在下面看到。</p><p>取得这一成功后， <em><a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/sophie-ellis-bextor-murder-on-the-dancefloor-saltburn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方排行榜</a></em>报道称，该曲目本周将重新进入前 40 名。目前在周中图表中位居第 27 位，预计本周将进一步上涨。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@sophieebtiktok/video/7318894979491925281" data-video-id="7318894979491925281" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;" ><section> <a target="_blank" title="@sophieebtiktok" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@sophieebtiktok?refer=embed">@sophieebtiktok</a></p><p>进入 2024 年，就像……索尔特伯恩新年快乐！ Xx <a title="舞池谋杀案" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/murderonthedancefloor?refer=embed">#murderonthedancefloor</a> <a title="索菲埃利斯贝斯特" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/sophieellisbextor?refer=embed">#sophieellisbextor</a><a title="盐烧电影" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/saltburnmovie?refer=embed">#saltburnmovie</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ sophs 可怕的编辑已经疯传 - sophie" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/sophs-awful-edit-thats-gone-viral-7245400589675727643?refer=embed">♬ sophs 可怕的编辑已经疯传 – sophie</a> </section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="苏菲·埃利斯-贝斯特 - 舞池谋杀案（修复版 4K）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/b7r4xxLzddA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em>《Saltburn</em> 》发行后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-ellis-bextor-responds-to-murder-on-the-dancefloor-resurgence-for-featuring-in-nsfw-saltburn-scene-3564527">埃利斯-贝斯特对她的热门单曲的复兴表示欢迎</a>，并在 X/Twitter 上写道：“哇……谢谢你们对 Murder 的热爱。新年快乐！ xx”。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-ellis-bextor-reacts-to-barry-keoghans-nude-dance-to-her-song-in-saltburn-3563684">歌手之前在谈到场景本身时表示，她“对视觉效果还没有做好准备”</a> 。 “直到我在放映时看到它，我才真正知道它在电影中的角色将如何发挥，但我绝对喜欢它，”她说。 “我认为这是一部非常聪明、有趣、聪明的电​​影。我真的很喜欢它。”</p><p>这位歌手补充说，她很高兴导演埃默拉尔德·芬内尔使用她的歌曲，因为他们对这部电影“并没有真正的 B 计划”。</p><p> “她只是觉得它把电影的基调和流行歌曲的甜蜜并置在一起，但也和歌词的尾部有点刺痛，”她说。 “我认为这有效。但这对我来说是多么可爱啊，我的意思是，你看，我唱《谋杀》已有 20 多年了，它是如此美妙，以至于它仍然有能力让我感到惊讶。”</p><p>这部电影以 2006 年为背景， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/saltburn-music-indie-pop-noughties-mgmt-bloc-party-3537593">充满了二十世纪九十年代的热门歌曲，</a>如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girls-aloud">Girls Aloud</a>的《Sound Of The Underground》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a>的《This Modern Love》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a>的《Mr Brightside》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/saltburn-review-party-with-the-poshos-in-the-naughty-noughties-3541554">在<em>《Saltburn》</em>的四星评论中</a>， <em>《NME》</em>将这部电影描述为“令人陶醉的新讽刺剧”，并补充道：“ <em>Saltburn</em>并不是今年最受关注的派对，但你仍然不应该错过它。”</p><p> Sophie Ellis-Bextor 的《Murder On The Dancefloor》继《Saltburn》场景首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-ellis-bextors-murder-on-the-dancefloor-to-return-to-top-40-chart-after-saltburn-scene-3565573">后重返排行榜前 40 名</a>。</p> ;
